<L>__{exterior castle hackton day}
<A>__{fifty, or so, servants have turned out to greet their mistress, and their new master. the land steward, who is the senior servant, introduces the others the clerk of the kitchen, clerk of the stables, head gardener, ladies in waiting, butler, valet, chef, cook.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{i had not arrived at the pitch of prosperity, and having, at thirty years of age, by my own merits and energy, raised myself to one of the highest social positions that any man in england could occupy, i determined to enjoy myself as becomes a man of quality for the remainder of my life.}
